{"word":"βόειος","slug":"βόειος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βόειος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βοῦς'><el>βοῦς</el></a>\n<p/><i>of an ox</i> or <i>oxen</i>, <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> <i>of ox-hide</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>; <el>βόεα κρέα</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>γάλα βόειον</el> <i>cows</i> milk, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>βόεια ρήματα</el> <i>great bull</i>- words (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>βούπαις</el>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>), <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}